x
A\cos x + B\sin x = C
A\cos x+B\sin x=C
A\neq 0, B\neq 0
\xi
\cos(\xi)=\frac{A}{\sqrt{A^2+B^2}},\sin(\xi)=\frac{B}{\sqrt{A^2+B^2}}
\frac{A}{\sqrt{A^2+B^2}}\cos x+\frac{B}{\sqrt{A^2+B^2}}\sin x=\frac{C}{\sqrt{A^2+B^2}}
\frac{A}{\sqrt{A^2+B^2}}\le1,~~\frac{B}{\sqrt{A^2+B^2}}\le1,~~\frac{C}{\sqrt{A^2+B^2}}\le1
